 MacKenzie Scott, the world’s 22nd richest person, and the world richest person, Jeff Bezos’s ex-wife has found love again, and has married a Seattle private school science teacher Dan Jewett, a school attended by her children. Mackenzie and the Amazon founder Jeff Bezos’s divorced in 2019, after which she became the world’s 22nd richest person. For Ms. Scott, her remarriage is the latest twist in a life where she has quietly but firmly set the limits of her own privacy.